Class User

java.lang.Object
com.group6.hms.app.managers.auth.User
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
Patient, Staff
public abstract class User extends Object implements Serializable
User is an abstract class for users in the system. It contains basic information about the user, including their unique ID, username, name, gender, and hashed password. Subclasses of User represent specific user roles within the system.
